REQUIREMENTS: 

 * Apache 2+ with MultiViews enabled. 

 * PHP5 support

 * MySQL 5 with one empty available database and a working user/password with
   basic permissions.

INSTALLATION:
 
 1. Edit configuration variables at the start of the script to suit your needs.

 2. Place the script in a web-accessible directory based on how you want it to
    be accessed. (For instance you can rename the file to blog.php, place it in
		the root of your webserver and can access it as http://example.com/blog)

 3. Open the script in a web browser.

 4. You can now begin adding articles via http://example.com/blog/admin.
